{"type": "article", "id": 18027, "title": "球形灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060713414965lCH1kYGLU3ij4b.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约的家具品牌 Kresse 是由两位设计师新成立的，他们发布了一组家具作品。其中的圆形桌灯像是多个圆形平面垂直相交，光线从里面照射出来，形成了层次感，酷似一个折纸灯笼。另配有一跟彩色的布线，可选黄、白、灰蓝、棕 4 种颜色搭配。这盏灯直径有 7 英寸，售价 110 美元，<a href=\"http://kressenyc.com/products/ivory-grid-desk-lamp?variant=7979701505#\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134147rw9OWyGKdV60vDkI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134147wIKMEHYQb4v3lFhi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134148vWkndEGcTpeuraNw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134148KFiUIhCbGx6Jnam7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}